The paper deals with the problem of learning an optimal feedback policy for a nonlinear stochastic dynamical system, which is a common problem in the fields of machine learning, control systems, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
